- REQUIREMENTS

  This software was developed and tested with the default Perl v5.12.4 distribution that ships with Mac OS X 10.8.4. 

  The following Perl modules are required:

    Pod::Usage
    Getopt::Long
    Cwd
    File::Find

  And the following are optional:

    File::Spec
    Term::ReadKey

  You can obtain all of these modules from CPAN at http://www.cpan.org/.

- INSTALLATION

  No installation is required. 

- USAGE

  You can view available options by running the script without any arguments:

    $ perl pccp.pl

